data.about: Reality Based Firearms Training and Functional strength and Conditioning online programs serving the South Florida area.
data.name: RealWorld Tactical
data.description:
RealWorld Tactical is a veteran operated business based out of South Florida, that provides urban focused firearms training for the armed responsible citizen, Security Professional, and Law Enforcement or Military Personnel. We also specialize in consulting and product development for the Law Enforcement industry. 

Founded by Director of Operations Tony Sentmanat a Marine Corps veteran and Law Enforcement SWAT Operator, with over 16 years of Real World experience.  He brings you the concept  of  " Survival of Urban Chaos through Armed Tactical Solutions", A philosophy and teaching concept based on his military and urban operational experience. At RealWorld Tactical we don't aim to make great shooters we strive to train the best armed problem solvers. We believe that any body can teach you how to shoot a gun, were here to teach you how to become the fastest thinker trained with a gun.

Our Product development division inspires to create the next revolutionary product for  law enforcement training and tactical product industry. We believe in the constant need to innovate with concepts designed using real world experience, so that we can create better options, equipment and training for the patrol officer on the streets, the tactical officer in specialty units and the officers in SWAT operations. So we will continue on this path,  to better the lives of those protecting our families and neighborhoods.

data.about: The official Quiz Club of College Of Engineering Guindy, Anna University.
data.name: Quizzers Anonymous
data.description:
"Cogito ergo sum" 
I think, therefore I am. - Rene Descartes. 

Fierce in competing, Ferocious at pouncing and Fraternal towards quizzing. From the pacy world of sports to mind boggling facts on science, from the glamorous world of Entertainment to the Serious world of Business, one can find all the information required in this page. 

Taking a leaf out of Chef Gusteau's, we believe that 'Anybody and Everybody can Quiz'. If you're a follower of any field, may it be the Pacy world of Sports to Mind boggling facts on Science or from the Glamorous world of Entertainment to the Serious world of Business, you can be a Quizzer. Qualitative, Uber-class, Incredible, and Zealous are some of the adjectives once can describe quizzing with.  

Dare the extra step, Dethrone your shyness and jump into the world of amazing excitements. Let quizzing fill every neuron of yours, let the thoughts meander, let your instincts come to the fore and let the adrenaline run through your blood, for at the end it does not what matter how what you knew, all that matters is how much you learnt.
